plot: The 1st & 4th episodes are Ciel in Wonderland. The 2nd ep Elizabeth invites a mystery woman whom is implied as the viewer as a guest to a ball at the Phantomhive mansion. The 3rd ep is a documentary with behind the scenes interviews with Ciel, Sebastion and the rest of BB2 cast. The 5th ep is The life and times in the Trancy household. The final ep is The story of Will the Reaper.
